featured_reviews.review_id:
The Salafi masjid managed by the Wisdom Islamic Organization of Kerala is a spectacular Masjid in the heart of the KSRTC - Railway station portion of the town of Thrissur.

Finely pasted carpets, greatly designed Wuzhu area along with restrooms, neatly managed interior of the Masjid, sophisticated devices and luxurious walls; this Masjid has that all that any super attractive Masjid should have.

A not-little parking space is available officially at the back of the Masjid, being wheelchair accessible, even though the stairs are obstacles in front of a wheelchair user but the doors of the Masjid are not, as the main hall is wheelchair accessible here.
